		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>You stretch out, lending some of your strength to others while also channeling it to yourself.</em></p><p><strong>No Action Cost</strong> - 1 Creature (60 ft.) - 1 Ki - Magical</p><p><em>Trigger: you use @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.rfkAaOhAsX1HQRuo]{Flurry of Blows}, @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.UMZY7HTxI0EvRjsT]{Step of the Wind}, or @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.sRA3vPbD6QUAkFZT]{Patient Defense}.</em></p><p>Target can use their <strong>reaction</strong> to do one of the following, depending on which ability you used:</p><ul><li><p><strong>Flurry of Blows:</strong> target makes one weapon attack.</p></li><li><p><strong>Step of the Wind:</strong> target moves up to their speed without provoking &amp;reference[opportunityattacks]{attacks of opportunity}.</p></li><li><p><strong>Patient Defense:</strong> target takes the &amp;reference[dodge] action.</p></li></ul>",
